modelVersions.description:

This version has expanded training data with distributed weights based on resolution as well as some personally cropped close ups of faces to give as accurate training data as possible why decreasing step count. If using the prompt 'solid eyes' alone the eye will still have white sclera but with no pupil adding the term 'colored sclera' applies the same color to the whole eye so no need to specify sclera color.
